  "subject": "Add unique snapshot Docker image tags to portal-ng repos",
  "commit_message": "Add unique snapshot Docker image tags to portal-ng repos\n\n- add docker-push-staging-tags.sh to tag and push versioned snapshot images\n- tags: {version}, {version}-STAGING-latest, {version}-{timestamp}\n- aligns with ONAP convention used by Maven-based projects (fabric8 plugin)\n- script is CI-agnostic (works with both Jenkins and GitHub Actions)\n\nIssue-ID: PORTALNG-180\nChange-Id: I20126757621d34cd3ae1a2e8f523a6ea00f0609c\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
